    "body": "PAPI never completes building; spack appears to hang on `filter_file`, running at 100% CPU.\r\n\r\n### Expected Result\r\nPAPI builds and installs.\r\n\r\n### Actual Result\r\nSpack hangs after filtering files, consuming 100% CPU on a single core.\r\nIt never appears to actually get to `make()`, from looking at the build log.\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n```console\r\n$ spack install papi\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Information on your system\r\n* Arch Linux\r\n* x86_64\r\n* glibc 2.26\r\n* GCC 7.3.0\r\n* Python 3.6.4\r\n",
